Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deselectPin(25.10)                                          deselectPin(25.10)

Name
       deselectPin - Deselects the specified pin

Syntax
       deselectPin

        [-help]

       <name>

       Deselects the specified pin.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes type and default infor-
              mation for each deselectPin parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man deselectPin

       <name> Specifies the name of the pin to be deselected.

Example
       The following example deselects the swack pin.

       deselectPin swack

Related Information
              * selectPin

